properties.areaDesc: Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI; Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI; Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 16 at 3:01PM CST until February 18 at 9:00AM CST by NWS Green Bay WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Waves 4 to 7 ft expected on Monday, subsiding later
Monday night. Gusts to 25 knots are also possible.

* WHERE...Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI, Sturgeon Bay
to Two Rivers WI and Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Monday to 9 AM CST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM MONDAY TO 9 AM CST TUESDAY
